main event: Two unidentified flying objects were observed at a missile site in Nebraska on 26 August 1965.
interesting points: The objects were described as bright spheres,The first sighting occurred at approximately 1430 hours with the objects moving at a high rate of speed,One consisted of two objects about one mile apart,The objects changed direction in a zigzag manner,The sighting lasted for approximately 2 minutes and 7 seconds.
witness description: Nine military personnel and two civilians from the 551st USAF Medical Group.
